Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Cholesterol discovery wins Nobel prize
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xnc7
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Oct 1985
University of Texas duo win Nobel prize for their work on cause of cholesterol build-up. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less